---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Nav from '../../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import { translations } from '../../i18n/translations';

const lang = 'en';
const t = translations[lang];
---

<BaseLayout lang={lang} title="Partner Programme Terms — Strategic Decision" description="Terms of participation in the Strategic Decision referral programme. Commissions, requirements, and how subscription discounts work.">
  <Nav t={t.nav} lang={lang} />
  <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-32">

    <div class="mb-10">
      <a href={`/${lang}/`} class="text-sm text-indigo-500 hover:text-indigo-400 transition-colors">&larr; Back to home</a>
    </div>

    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 dark:text-white tracking-tight mb-3">
      Partner Programme Terms
    </h1>
    <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm mb-12">Last updated: April 2025</p>

    <div class="prose prose-slate dark:prose-invert max-w-none space-y-10 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">1. How the programme works</h2>
        <p>
          The Strategic Decision Partner Programme allows anyone to generate a unique referral link and share it with professionals in their network. When someone registers and subscribes to a paid plan through that link, the partner earns a <strong class="text-slate-900 dark:text-white">20% commission</strong> on the referred client's monthly fee, for as long as that client maintains an active subscription.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">2. Key requirement: invoicing capability</h2>
        <p>
          To receive commissions as cash payments, the partner must be a <strong class="text-slate-900 dark:text-white">registered self-employed person or business professional</strong> with the legal capacity to issue invoices in their country of residence.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3">
          If you meet this requirement, commissions will be paid monthly upon receipt of your invoice to Strategic Decision, once a minimum accumulated threshold of €20 has been reached.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">3. Can't invoice? Discount on your subscription</h2>
        <p>
          If you are an employee, a private individual without a registered business activity, or anyone without the legal capacity to issue an invoice, <strong class="text-slate-900 dark:text-white">you cannot receive commissions as cash</strong>. In that case, any commissions you generate are automatically applied as a <strong class="text-slate-900 dark:text-white">discount on your own monthly Strategic Decision subscription</strong>, under the following conditions:
        </p>
        <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 list-none pl-0">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-indigo-500 font-bold mt-0.5">—</span>
            <span><strong class="text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Maximum: 100% of your monthly fee.</strong> The discount never exceeds your subscription amount. You never pay more than your plan costs and never receive cash.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-indigo-500 font-bold mt-0.5">—</span>
            <span><strong class="text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Non-cumulative between months.</strong> Any discount not applied in the current month does not carry over to the next. Unused amounts are forfeited at the end of each billing period.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-indigo-500 font-bold mt-0.5">—</span>
            <span><strong class="text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Practical example:</strong> If your plan is €99/month and you have generated €150 in commissions that month, a €99 discount is applied (bringing your fee to €0). The remaining €51 is not carried over or paid out — it is cancelled at the close of the billing period.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">4. Fair use policy</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2 list-none pl-0">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-indigo-500 font-bold mt-0.5">—</span>
            <span>Self-referrals are not permitted. You may not refer yourself or any accounts you directly or indirectly control.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-indigo-500 font-bold mt-0.5">—</span>
            <span>Spam, unsolicited bulk messaging, or deceptive promotion of your referral link is prohibited.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-indigo-500 font-bold mt-0.5">—</span>
            <span>Strategic Decision reserves the right to terminate participation in the programme for any fraudulent or abusive conduct, without prior notice and without obligation to pay any outstanding commissions.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">5. Programme changes</h2>
        <p>
          Strategic Decision may modify the programme terms at any time (commission rate, thresholds, payment timelines, etc.) with at least 30 days' notice to active partners. Continued participation after the notice period constitutes acceptance of the updated terms.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">6. Contact</h2>
        <p>
          For any questions about the programme, contact us at <a href="mailto:info@strategicdecision.ai" class="text-indigo-500 hover:text-indigo-400 underline">info@strategicdecision.ai</a>.
        </p>
      </section>

    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer t={t.footer} lang={lang} />
</BaseLayout>
